* CD info
Charpentier - Extremum dei judicium (Judgment Day) and Miserere des Jesuites - Michel Corboz &amp; Soli - Erato, 1974

* About the recording
This recording is very hard to find, and contains an incredible rendition of Charpentier's religious works. If you are used to baroque music played by baroque ensembles, you will be surprised by the way Corboz appropriate this music! It is completely over-dramatic, sumptuous display of piety, as opposed to the usual austere interpretations.

